## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

All tests are designed to run offline with mocked LLM responses.

**Run the entire red-team suite:**
```bash
cd /Users/mk/Documents/chatbot-ai-systems-production

# Backend (Pytest) — all 3 layers
PYTHONPATH=src pytest tests/redteam/ -v --tb=short -x

# Frontend (Playwright) — Layer 1
cd frontend && npx playwright test tests/redteam/ --reporter=list
```

**Run individual layers:**
```bash
# Layer 2: Backend
PYTHONPATH=src pytest tests/redteam/backend/ -v

# Layer 3: Agentic
PYTHONPATH=src pytest tests/redteam/agentic/ -v

# Layer 4: MCP/Tools
PYTHONPATH=src pytest tests/redteam/tools/ -v
```

### Manual Verification
- Review the test plan document at `docs/phase_8.0.md` for completeness
- Confirm all tests pass with `0 failures` on first run
- Verify no real API calls (Ollama, Redis, MCP servers) are made during test execution by checking test logs
